<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>PRS comment generator</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>PRS order helper</h1>


            <div class="description-section">
                <h2>This tool will help make the comment text in PRS quicker</h2>
                <div class="instruction-section">
                    <!-- <h3>Instructions</h3> -->
                    <ul>
                        <li>It uses a template spreadsheet with your information and gives you a text file</li>
                        <li>It will sort through all the different suppliers and group the info together</li>
                        <li>You can't change the names for the column headers, but you can move them around the top row
                        </li>
                        <li>Don't delete the red compulsary column headers</li>
                        <li>If you don't have a value for optional entries (e.g. GIX numbers), you can delete that
                            header</li>
                        <li>Upload your spreadsheet using the upload button</li>
                        <li>Press submit to get your text file. If successful you will get a download</li>
                        <li>If you see things like "NaN" for numbers, your entries are most likely text. Change them to
                            numbers in the spreadsheet and upload and sumbit again</li>
                    </ul>

                </div>
                <p>Download a copy of the template using the button below</p>
                <a href="/Input_file_template.xlsx" class="btn" download>Get template spreadsheet</a>

                <div class="error-section">

                    <% if (locals.message) { %>
                    <h2><%= message %></h2>
                    <% } %>

                </div>
            </div>



            <div class="form-section">
                <form action="/upload" method="post" id="form" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <div class="input-section">
                        <p>Upload your spreadsheet with the button below</p>


                        <input type="file" name="file" id="file-upload" accept=".xlsx">


                        <p>Press submit to get the text file</p>
                        <button class="btn big-btn" type="submit">Submit</button>

                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </body>

</html>